406
00:23:11,470 --> 00:23:14,680
弟弟 拜托 这太荒唐了
Brother, please. This is high folly.

407
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:16,290
过去的几周里你已经屠杀了那么多人
Is it not enough that you have slaughtered

