难道还不够么？
dozens in just these past several weeks?

409
00:23:18,020 --> 00:23:18,560
这个嘛...
Well--

410
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:20,210
城里堆满尸体的流言
Word of a city littered with bodies

411
