Well, well, well.

460
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:24,590
伟大的Marcel
The great Marcel,

461
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:27,710
自称为新奥尔良国王之人
self-proclaimed king of New Orleans,

462
00:28:27,710 --> 00:28:29,770
