This town isn't for everybody.

498
00:30:30,590 --> 00:30:31,820
离开吧
Please.

499
00:30:37,380 --> 00:30:39,240
我敢肯定你有很多的疑问
I'm sure you got questions.

500
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:41,030
也就一千多个吧
Only a thousand of them,

501
